extracted_text: A. Minimum Gross Land Area: 5,000 square feet (see Subsection 14.03.02)
llm_outputs.rationale: The document provides two different values for the minimum lot size of the E4 district. On page 252, it states 5,000 square feet, while on page 587 it lists 21,780 sq ft.
